  "page": "A Storm of Swords-Chapter 27",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;background-color:rgb(35, 135, 75)\">Daenerys III</th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords\" title=\"A Storm of Swords\">A Storm of Swords</a></i> chapter</td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-image\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/A_storm_of_swords\" title=\"A storm of swords\"><img alt=\"AStormOfSwords.jpg\" src=\"/images/thumb/2/24/AStormOfSwords.jpg/220px-AStormOfSwords.jpg\" width=\"220\" height=\"353\" class=\"thumbborder\" srcset=\"/images/2/24/AStormOfSwords.jpg 1.5x\" /></a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">POV</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Daenerys_Targaryen\" title=\"Daenerys Targaryen\">Daenerys</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Place</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Astapor\" title=\"Astapor\">Astapor</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Page</th><td>\n304 <small>UK HC</small> <small>(<a href=\"/index.php/Chapters_Table_of_contents\" title=\"Chapters Table of contents\">Other versions</a>)</small></td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;background-color:rgb(35, 135, 75)\">Chapter chronology <small>(<a href=\"/index.php/Chapters\" title=\"Chapters\">All</a>)</small></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_23\" title=\"A Storm of Swords-Chapter 23\">Daenerys II</a><br />↑</td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<table style=\"width:100%;\"><tbody><tr>\n<td style=\"width:33%; text-align:center; vertical-align:middle;\"><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_26\" title=\"A Storm of Swords-Chapter 26\">Jon III</a></td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:middle;\">&#160;←</td>\n<td style=\"width:33%; text-align:center; vertical-align:middle; padding-right:0.1em; padding-left:0.1em;\"><a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Daenerys III</a></td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:middle;\">→&#160;</td>\n<td style=\"width:33%; text-align:center; vertical-align:middle;\"><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_28\" title=\"A Storm of Swords-Chapter 28\">Sansa III</a></td>\n</tr></tbody></table></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n↓<br /><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_42\" title=\"A Storm of Swords-Chapter 42\">Daenerys IV</a></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Synopsis\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Synopsis</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Character_List\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Character List</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Places_and_Terms_Mentioned\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Places and Terms Mentioned</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#References_and_Notes\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References and Notes</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Synopsis\">Synopsis</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_27&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Synopsis\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p><a href=\"/index.php/Daenerys_Targaryen\" title=\"Daenerys Targaryen\">Daenerys</a> tells the slavers that she wants all eight thousand <a href=\"/index.php/Unsullied\" title=\"Unsullied\">Unsullied</a>, plus all the slave boys in training, whether they've been cut yet or not. In order to pay the slave masters, Daenerys offers all three of her ships as well as <a href=\"/index.php/Drogon\" title=\"Drogon\">Drogon</a>, for the price of a dragon is incalculable. Daenerys frees <a href=\"/index.php/Missandei\" title=\"Missandei\">Missandei</a> and takes her into her service, revealing that she can speak <a href=\"/index.php/High_Valyrian\" title=\"High Valyrian\">High Valyrian</a>. We learn that <a href=\"/index.php/Valar_Morghulis\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Valar Morghulis\">Valar Morghulis</a> means 'all men must die'. \n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tleft\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:302px;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:David_Sondered_A_Dragon_is_no_Slave.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/9/97/David_Sondered_A_Dragon_is_no_Slave.jpg/300px-David_Sondered_A_Dragon_is_no_Slave.jpg\" width=\"300\" height=\"313\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/9/97/David_Sondered_A_Dragon_is_no_Slave.jpg/450px-David_Sondered_A_Dragon_is_no_Slave.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/9/97/David_Sondered_A_Dragon_is_no_Slave.jpg/600px-David_Sondered_A_Dragon_is_no_Slave.jpg 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:David_Sondered_A_Dragon_is_no_Slave.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Art by David Sondered © Fantasy Flight Games</div></div></div>\n<p>That night, <a href=\"/index.php/Quaithe\" title=\"Quaithe\">Quaithe</a> appears to Daenerys, seemingly in a dream, telling her again, \"To go north, you must journey south. To reach the west, you must go east. To go forward you must go back, and to touch the light you must pass beneath the shadow.\" When the time for the deal to be brokered arrives, Daenerys swings the slaver's whip in <a href=\"/index.php/Kraznys_mo_Nakloz\" title=\"Kraznys mo Nakloz\">Kraznys</a>' face, and releases Drogon on him, shouting, \"Drogon! Dracarys!\" This is the sign for her followers to attack the slavers. With the help of the Unsullied who obey her as she is now their owner she has the slavers killed. The other slaves join her and soon <a href=\"/index.php/Astapor\" title=\"Astapor\">Astapor</a> is conquered. \n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Character_List\">Character List</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_27&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Character List\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<table class=\"wikitable\" width=\"70%\">\n\n<tbody><tr valign=\"top\">\n<td style=\"width:33;\">\n<p><b>Appearing:</b>\n</p>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Daenerys_Targaryen\" title=\"Daenerys Targaryen\">Daenerys Targaryen</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Missandei\" title=\"Missandei\">Missandei</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Grazdan_mo_Ullhor\" title=\"Grazdan mo Ullhor\">Grazdan</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Irri\" title=\"Irri\">Irri</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Jhiqui\" title=\"Jhiqui\">Jhiqui</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Barristan_Selmy\" title=\"Barristan Selmy\">Whitebeard</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Belwas\" title=\"Belwas\">Belwas</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Aggo\" title=\"Aggo\">Aggo</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Jhogo\" title=\"Jhogo\">Jhogo</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Rakharo\" title=\"Rakharo\">Rakharo</a></li></ul>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width:33;\">\n<p><b>Appearing:</b>\n</p>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Jorah_Mormont\" title=\"Jorah Mormont\">Jorah Mormont</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Kraznys_mo_Nakloz\" title=\"Kraznys mo Nakloz\">Kraznys mo Nakloz</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Drogon\" title=\"Drogon\">Drogon</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Viserion\" title=\"Viserion\">Viserion</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Rhaegal\" title=\"Rhaegal\">Rhaegal</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Groleo\" title=\"Groleo\">Groleo</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Quaithe\" title=\"Quaithe\">Quaithe</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/The_Silver\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"The Silver\">The Silver</a></li></ul>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width:33;\">\n<p><b>Mentioned:</b>\n</p>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Grazdan_(Great)\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Grazdan (Great)\">Grazdan the Great</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Viserys_Targaryen\" title=\"Viserys Targaryen\">Viserys Targaryen</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Rhaella_Targaryen\" title=\"Rhaella Targaryen\">Rhaella Targaryen</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Aegon_I_Targaryen\" title=\"Aegon I Targaryen\">Aegon I Targaryen</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Aerys_II_Targaryen\" title=\"Aerys II Targaryen\">Aerys II Targaryen</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Eroeh\" title=\"Eroeh\">Eroeh</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Drogo\" title=\"Drogo\">Khal Drogo</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Mago\" title=\"Mago\">Mago</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Robert_Baratheon\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Robert Baratheon\">Robert Baratheon</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Rhaegar_Targaryen\" title=\"Rhaegar Targaryen\">Rhaegar Targaryen</a></li></ul>\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Places_and_Terms_Mentioned\">Places and Terms Mentioned</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_27&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Places and Terms Mentioned\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<table class=\"wikitable\" width=\"100%\">\n\n<tbody><tr valign=\"top\">\n<td style=\"width:33;\">\n<p><b>Places:</b>\n</p>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Qarth\" title=\"Qarth\">Qarth</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Astapor\" title=\"Asta